We make building as enjoyable as buying and selling online.
Meet Bolster, a challenger in construction management software, revolutionizing the way residential construction is bought, sold and managed.
Bolster’s Journey
Originally founded as CostCertified, the platform was born out of a frustration with outdated estimation processes and a lack of digital solutions. This challenge sparked the innovation behind a platform that’s now leading the way in transforming the construction industry.

In 2021, Bolster broke Alberta records for the highest seed round fundraising after completing Y Combinator - the world’s most exclusive startup incubator program.
Building the future
As we grow, Bolster is committed to delivering new products and features at the forefront of the evolving needs of our customers and the industry. We strive to push boundaries and pioneer new approaches, elevating industry standards and working with our clients to deliver exceptional results.
